2008-12-30  Matthias Clasen  <mclasen@redhat.com>

	Bug 565310 – support hotkeys for a11y tools

	* configure.ac: Set MATE_KEYBINDINGS_KEYSDIR.

	* data/mate-settings-daemon.schemas.in: Add missing schemas for
	the keys in /destkop/mate/applications/at, and also add new
	schemas for keys in /desktop/mate/keybindings that define 
	global keybindings for turning ATs on and off. Todo: There are no
	default key combinations in the schema yet.

