	file for building against an uninstalled copy of g-s-d (bug #511820)

2008-02-05  Jens Granseuer  <jensgr@gmx.net>

	Based on a patch by: Damien Carberry <damien carberry@sun.com>

	* Makefile.am:
	* autogen.sh:
	* configure.ac:
	* plugins/a11y-keyboard/Makefile.am:
